BusFusionites, the BusFusion website has been updated with a full report
including a few pics of the event.  From the main menu choose "BusFusion 2003"
then "Report & Pics".  Go check it out for memories or what you missed.  Any
of you who have pictures that you'd like to share but do not have a space to
load them on the web let me know.  Those of you who have space and have them
on the web please provide me with the link so I can post it to the BusFusion
site.  Enjoy and see you all at BusFusion 2004 !

